	<rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/54i#Influencer"/>
	<rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">External or internal factor that influences the enterprise in focus. That could be a policy of another country, the oil price etc. It could be a constraint, or an opportunity. In any case it is something that cannon be directly influenced by the enterprise in focus.

An example of internal factor is maturity, or the age pyramid.</rdfs:comment>
	<rdfs:isDefinedBy rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/54i#"/>
